    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though the engine idles a bit rough and it will likely need a tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been well-used but still has life left in it.",
