    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard and preserved in showroom condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an interior and exterior entirely free of discernible wear. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically impeccable, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning driver who demands excellence. Every detail has been rigorously scrutinized to ensure it meets our highest benchmarks for quality and presentation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
