    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've really got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in incredible shape\u2014looks and drives just like it did the day I picked it up! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, keeping it garaged and sparkling clean at all times. It\u2019s a total gem and I\u2019m a bit sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
