    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage and there isn't a single blemish to be found. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
