      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of the A80 platform. This specimen retains its factory-original 2JZ-GTE power plant, featuring the sequential twin-turbocharged configuration and cast-iron block known for exceptional thermal efficiency and structural integrity. Mated to the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains unmodified and mechanically synchronized. The suspension geometry utilizes factory double-wishbones for precise lateral stiffness and optimal contact patches. With a documented service history, verifiable matching numbers, and a chassis free of structural fatigue, this vehicle represents a rare, investment-grade opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak JDM performance.",
